JOHANNESBURG - Winter is here.Â Snow has fallen in parts of Lesotho and the transformation is breathtaking. Parts of Afriski in Lesotho is a winter wonderland. Snow also fell around the Tiffindell Ski Resort near Rhodes in the Eastern Cape. More snow has been forecast to fall across parts of the Eastern Cape, KwaZulu-Natal, the Lesotho Drakensberg and the Maluti Mountain range in Lesotho over the coming days.